	<h1 class="title">据说这部《星球大战：原力觉醒》&quot;热血沸腾，不灭人性&quot;</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Manohla Dargis</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-19 07:20:52 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19392/medium/19392.jpg?1450435033" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="19392" data-title="《据说这部《星球大战：原力觉醒》&quot;热血沸腾，不灭人性&quot;》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/19392/medium/19392.jpg?1450435033" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/19392.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
